24 y1bb ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">When Peter saw their astonishment, what </div><div class="t m729 x73 h24 y1bc ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">did he say? Verse 12. </div><div class="t m1377 x60 h24 y1bd ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to. To whom did he at once direct their minds? </div><div class="t m1f9 x74 h24 y106 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Verse 13. </div><div class="t m354 x34 h24 y107 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. To what particular thing in connection with </div><div class="t m55b x74 h24 y108 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ did he refer? Verses 14, 15. </div><div class="t m25e x60 h24 y10a ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">12. </div><div class="t m7fc x49 h24 y10a ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Was it for the purpose of taunting them that </div><div class="t m667 x74 h24 y10b ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Peter referred to the crucifixion of Christ? Verse </div><div class="t mcad x74 h24 y369 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">17. </div><div class="t m25e x60 h24 y477 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">13. </div><div class="t mc9 x59 h24 y477 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What fact did he want especially to impress </div><div class="t m1645 x74 h24 y6e ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">on their minds? Verse 15, last part. </div><div class="t m25e x60 h24 y21 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">14. </div><div class="t m376 x59 h24 y21 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What power did he then say had made the </div><div class="t mac0 x74 h24 y184 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lame man whole? Verse 16. </div><div class="t m25e x60 h24 y8fa ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">15. </div><div class="t m681 x59 h24 y8fa ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Because of the humility of Jesus, what has </div><div class="t m1dc x74 h24 y5bc ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">he received? Phil. 2:9, to. </div><div class="t m25e x60 h24 y79 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">16. </div><div class="t m19f9 x59 h24 y1e3 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What was it that gave the lame man the per-</div><div class="t m137a x74 h24 y8c6 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fect soundness?&apos; Acts 3:16, last part. </div><div class="t m25e x60 h24 yf1 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">17. </div><div class="t m6e6 x59 h24 y38 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Is there anything else that comes by the </div><div class="t m376 x74 h24 y972 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">faith of Jesus Christ? Rom 3:22; Phil. 3:9. </div><div class="t m25e x60 h24 y885 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">18. </div><div class="t me73 x50 h24 yca ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Did the min who received strength by faith </div><div class="t m6d7 x61 h24 y881 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">have actual power, or only imaginary power? </div><div class="t m76d x61 h24 ye1e ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Acts 3:8, 16. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
